    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;When logged in to ODE, clicking on the ToS link in the footer generates a 404 (you are not authorized) error.  When not logged in, clicking on the ToS link in the footer takes you to the login page.&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;In both cases, it should render the ToS.&lt;/p&gt;    </content>
